PrecisAppointment (a) of Chief Justice BENJAMIN HEWAK as Administrator of the Government of Manitoba, who shall execute the office and functions of the Lieutenant Governor of Manitoba during the absence, illness or other inability of the Lieutenant Governor; and (b) of Mr. Justice A. KERR TWADDLE as temporary Administrator, who shall execute the same office over the course of a two day period in March 1990 (March 1-2).
